snippet.title: Kena Bridge of Spirits - PS5 Developer presentation - Future Games Show
snippet.description: Kena Bridge of Spirits is coming this hoilday for PS5 and on the Epic game store. We caught up with the developers to find out more about it in this exclusive interview.
